 les nombreux aspects techniques et scientifiques de la conservation des esp\u00e8ces et consacre ses efforts \u00e0 pr\u00e9server la diversit\u00e9 biologique. La CSE apporte une contribution notable aux accords internationaux relatifs \u00e0 la conservation de la diversit\u00e9 biologique. https://www.uicn.org/theme/species/about/species- survival-commission TRAFFIC, le r\u00e9seau de surveillance continue du commerce de la faune et de la flore sauvages, a pour mission de s\u2019assurer que le commerce des plantes et des animaux sauvages ne nuit pas \u00e0 la conservation de la nature. TRAFFIC est une alliance strat\u00e9gique entre l\u2019UICN et le WWF. http://www.traffic.org", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "9f7a5508-c8a6-4242-bd7e-8cfb7ccc2c3c": {"__data__": {"id_": "9f7a5508-c8a6-4242-bd7e-8cfb7ccc2c3c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/analisis-de-las-propuestas-de-enmienda-los-apendices-de-cites-de", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "An\u00e1lisis de las propuestas de enmienda a los ap\u00e9ndices de CITES de UICN/TRAFFIC para la 17e Reuni\u00f3n de la Conferencia de la Partes", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/es/resources/literatura-gris/analisis-de-las-propuestas-de-enmienda-los-apendices-de-cites-de", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "feed8982d882e3dcc1241136a5a3c1ee31289347290f35578c6633489a9e7f1a"}, "3": {"node_id": "afa7f664-4c02-4d27-90bb-4592013d85b8", "node_type": null, "metadata"